e":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T18:16:00.000Z","msg":"泛民既記者會 有咩討論空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地都知自己冇可能否決到 出黎舉下牌又收工<br />\n巴打第一次睇政治新聞？<br />\n依個模式玩左十幾年架啦wo<br />\n衰d講 追八卦新聞都話有花生食下<br />\n睇泛民搞所謂「抗爭」 只係睇住一場又一場早註定結果既鬧劇 仲要睇到一肚氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e525763563c94e3f9c7fe92d0ced6af027bcc097","tid":1110803,"uid":233050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T18:46:58.000Z","msg":"有無諗過根本唔洗轉移<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為港豬都係唔會理"},{"pid":"9845e520a7d357472e6ce5538922b1a3dd5cfa6c","tid":1110803,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:42:53.000Z","msg":"關乜事<br />\n香港人本性如此"},{"pid":"eed8dc50d3fcfb4041bfd2f610dde84ed46c9777","tid":1110803,"uid":125755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:48:32.000Z","msg":"但理智咁講，就算琴日無安心事件出黎，逃犯條例受到全城關注，咁有點！？<br />\n<br />\n巴打你覺得有群眾壓力下政府唔會格硬黎，但事實係，由逃犯條例推出黎開始，政府就一直格硬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa784919423b2bfda06e58d0389ac7803e2232a","tid":1110803,"uid":6548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:51:07.000Z","msg":"真係天真過天真嬌"},{"pid":"ac30518d2e0a690dc519bebcc9ba47cef0cdeb25","tid":1110803,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:54:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3995f8e932c56e34f5604220b02afae789334e9a","tid":1110803,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:56:07.000Z","msg":"引導你去汶萊伊朗，亂石掟死"}]}